      "@type": "Article",
      "headline": "Blox Fruits Trade Value Calculator",
      "description": "Calculate and compare the exact community trade values of different Blox Fruits to ensure you are getting fair deals and avoiding scams.",
      "author": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "SiliconBased"
